{"tid":2087732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港公署稱港區國安法公布實施是大事好事喜事","createTime":"2020-06-30T19:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T20:23:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fc108eeae53ea209ddd1a6c32f1302231424f0a3","tid":2087732,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:42:16.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港特派員公署發表聲明，表示堅決擁護和支持《港區國安法》的公布實施，形容是「一國兩制」方針在香港實踐進程中的大事、好事、喜事。<br />\n<br />\n聲明重申，香港是中國的香港，香港事務純屬中國內政，任何人都不要低估中國政府，維護國家主權安全的決心；又指任何干擾和阻撓《港區國安法》實施的企圖，都將遭到包括香港同胞在內的14億中國人民堅決反對，國際社會應該為維護香港繁榮穩定和「一國兩制」行穩致遠，發揮建設性作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535057-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535057-20200701.htm&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=38af9ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535057-20200701.htm&h=a647f206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535057-20200701.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1ed40a5128f6b17532a9c377a9c453a33fe3d43d","tid":2087732,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔立由至可<br />\n一立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac610b96a38b7f0a041a7e59d1d1934e97d49f70","tid":2087732,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:46:38.000Z","msg":"幫佢哋老母做白事"},{"pid":"d1d5beb3947d93df4a52080f69f62f63dadb2a1c","tid":2087732,"uid":15605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"華南水災是大事、好事、喜事。"},{"pid":"3c80e6d268194bb69a1f3328d8b89d82246ed41a","tid":2087732,"uid":241742,"like":3,"dislike"